<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>My Portfolio</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Manasa Portfolio</h1>
        <p>Data Analyst | CSE Student</p>
    </header>

    <section>
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>I am a passionate student aiming to become a Data Analyst.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Projects</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Smart Waste Management System</li>
